#* '''2002''', James A. Duke (editor), ''CRC Handbook of Medicinal Spices'', [http://books.google.com.au/books?id=g_OCl6P0vsYC&pg=PA129&dq=%22saffron%22%7C%22saffrons%22&hl=en&sa=X&ei=mAOHU4PEFJCtkgWF5YGgAQ&redir_esc=y#v=onepage&q=%22saffron%22%7C%22saffrons%22&f=false page 129],
